name: 15 Overheads at Los Angeles International Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Ok, so I lied about my LAX videos being finished. I have one last one for you guys, a short compilation of overheads shot from the classic In-N-Out Burger spotting location. Listen to the variety of engine sounds from all these different aircrafts! Hope you enjoy, and stay tuned for something new tomorrow ;)
